                    <msContents>
                        <summary>AM 241 a I fol. is a new shelfmark. In <date when="1996"
                                >1996</date> the shelfmark AM 241 a fol. was divided into AM 241 a I
                            fol. and <ref type="ms" target="AM02-0241-a-II-en">AM 241 a II
                                fol.</ref> and this part was furthermore reconstructed from leaves
                            belonging to three different manuscripts: Ff. 7-15, 18-19, 24, 26-27 and
                            30-42 originate from AM 241 a fol., ff. 1-6 are taken from AM 249 p fol.
                            and ff. 16-17, 20-23, 25 and 28-29 from <ref type="ms" target="#Acc-0007-d-en">Acc. 7 d, Hs.
                                106</ref>.</summary>
                        <msItem n="1" class="salm bibls">
