                    <history>
                        <origin>Written in <origPlace>Iceland</origPlace>
                            <origDate notBefore="1315" notAfter="1335">c. 1325</origDate>. It is
                            possible that the illumination was made in Norway. The psalter once
                            consisted of 88 leaves of which only 35 are still extant and ten of them
                            were used as binding material for other manuscripts.</origin>
